<div class='jumbotron'>
  <div class='container text-center'>
    <h1>Listed</h1>
    <p>Create and share lists for <em>everything</em></p>

    <% if current_user %>
      <%= link_to 'Create', new_list_path, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary' %>
    <% else %>
      <%= link_to 'Signup', 'signup', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary' %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='container'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <h2>What is Listed?</h2>

      <p class='lead'>Listed is an online platform for creating and sharing lists of content. On Listed, you can create lists which are collections of items. You can share lists like your favorite albums, favorite movies, reasons for things, and more</p>
    </div>

    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <h2>Why Join Listed</h2>

      <p class='lead'>By joining Listed, you'll be able to create your own lists and comment on others. In addition, you can show your appreciation for lists by liking them.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <h2>Top Lists</h2>

      <div class='list-group'>
        <%= render 'lists/collection', lists: @top %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <h2>Recent Lists</h2>

      <div class='list-group'>
        <%= render 'lists/collection', lists: @recent %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>